data.description: Charming ranch style property with all features the new owner could ask for! This property features nice equity that can be stepped into just by making cosmetic updates. Nice sized living room and separate dining with many ways to mix and match furniture. Nice sized primary bathroom. Kitchen appliances, washer and dryer all will be included in the sale. Large open basement partially finished and many of the features can be kept including the nice lighting hanging from above. Newer roof central air cooling, and a detached 2 car garage that does feature an electric garage opener. Property also features a nice sized backyard perfect for gatherings and family events!
